Question: Denentech Electronic Technology Co., Ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Denentech Electronic Technology Co., Ltd.

Product Highlight: CES 2024

- Denentech will participate in the Consumer Electronics Show (CES) from January 9 to 12, 2024, showcasing innovative connector products and high-quality cable solutions at booth Westgate 2222.

- Products on display include pin headers, female headers, pogo pin connectors, etc.

- Denentech specializes in computer and electronic board-to-board, wire-to-board precision connectors and connector cable assemblies.

- The company also provides customized services, offering tailored solutions to meet customer needs.

- The company's professional team will introduce the high-performance connector product series in detail, demonstrating functional features, application scenarios, and technological innovations.

- Denentech welcomes global partners to discuss cooperation opportunities and share resources for mutual benefit and win-win results.
